Roberts is said to have been 'procured' for him by convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein, a billionaire American financier, who she accuses of using her as a 'sex slave'.

Maxwell, 53, was also accused in the legal papers, filed in Florida, of acting as a 'madame' and supplying young girls for Epstein and her friends. 

One picture, said to have been taken by Epstein during Andrew's first encounter with the girl in March 2001 shows the Prince with his arm around her waist as Maxwell looks on.  

